snippet.title: Pikmin 2 New Year Trailer
snippet.description:
The trailer for Pikmin 2 New Year
(Currently at version 1.38)

Featuring reverse-season overworld areas, new story caves, new cave styles and visuals, custom enemy textures etc.

Also featuring 30 new challenge mode stages, half of them are returning Cave Net caves of mine.

Download link: https://mega.nz/folder/2RZwXBjD#RfltmYKEg3KJ_iIuaWXXQA

Gamecube Nodtool Version: https://mega.nz/folder/PJQzUbBC#-NtZGVoF87d47CZEYFDxhg

Wii Version: https://mega.nz/folder/7YYH3BxS#tDRi3J03HAU-6ir0Dj8hKg

Website: https://amigaowlromhacks.wordpress.com/
